sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator<br/>Service Account
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>mTLS
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,RayHead: Flow 1: Interactive RayCluster Lifecycle
        User->>SDK: Cluster(config).up()
        SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1 RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster created

        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRs<br/>Auth: Service Account
        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create head-svc, worker pods<br/>Ports: 6379, 8265, 10001

        opt Kueue Integration
            SDK->>K8sAPI: List LocalQueues<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Default queue name
            Note over SDK: Adds kueue.x-k8s.io/queue-name label
        end

        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Secret {cluster}-ca-secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA cert + key

        SDK->>SDK: Generate client mTLS certs<br/>RSA 3072-bit, SHA-256<br/>Store ~/.local/share/codeflare/tls/

        SDK->>RayHead: GET /api/version (readiness)<br/>8265/TCP HTTPS mTLS
        RayHead-->>SDK: Dashboard ready

        User->>SDK: ray.init()
        SDK->>RayHead: Ray Client Protocol<br/>10001/TCP mTLS client cert
        RayHead-->>SDK: Connected
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,Kueue: Flow 2: RayJob Batch Submission
        User->>SDK: RayJob(config).submit()

        opt Local Files
            SDK->>SDK: Package entrypoint + working_dir<br/>zip + base64 encode
            SDK->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret {job}-files<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Secret created
        end

        opt Kueue Priority
            SDK->>K8sAPI: GET WorkloadPriorityClass<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Priority class validated
        end

        SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1 RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob created

        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CRs
        KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create managed RayCluster<br/>(if cluster_config provided)

        loop Poll Status
            SDK->>K8sAPI: GET RayJob status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: deploymentStatus, jobStatus
        end
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over SDK,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Dashboard URL Discovery (RHOAI 3.x)
        SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST HTTPRoutes<br/>label: ray.io/cluster-name
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: HTTPRoute found

        alt HTTPRoute found
            SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Gateway CR<br/>gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Gateway hostname
        else Fallback: OpenShift Route
            SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST Routes<br/>route.openshift.io/v1
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Route host
        else Fallback: GatewayConfig
            SDK->>K8sAPI: GET GatewayConfig CR<br/>services.platform.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1
            K8sAPI-->>SDK: Domain for URL construction
        end

        SDK->>SDK: Construct dashboard URL<br/>https://{host}/ray/{ns}/{cluster}
        SDK-->>User: Dashboard URL
    end
